{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你等一等，先等一等。","tone":"焦急","chapter":2,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"还等什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":14,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"就算你真的要想，我们至少也先说说话，聊聊天。","tone":"恳求","chapter":2,"line_start":18,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"现在我不想聊天。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":2,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"难道你也不想知道我为什么找你来？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"现在不想。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":2,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"你投不投降？","tone":"得意","chapter":2,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"不投降！","tone":"激动","chapter":2,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"你投降我就饶了你！","tone":"得意","chapter":2,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"我偏不投降，看你能把我怎么样？","tone":"激动","chapter":2,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"原来你真的不是个好人。","tone":"调侃","chapter":2,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"我本来就不是，尤其是在遇见你这种人的时候。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":2,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你知道我是什么人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"完全不知道？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"我只知道你非但也不是个好人，而且比我更坏，坏一百倍。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":2,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"但我却知道你。","tone":"微笑","chapter":2,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"完全知道？","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你叫小马，别人都叫你渔怒的小马，因为你的脾气比谁都大。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"对。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"你有个好朋友叫丁喜，聪明的丁喜。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"对。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"本来你们两个人总是形影不离的，可是现在他已有了老婆，人家恩爱夫妻，你当然不好意思再夹在人家中间了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"本来你也有个女人，你认为她一定会嫁给你的，她本来也准备嫁给你的，只可惜你的脾气太大，竟把她气跑了。你找了三个月，却连她的影子都找不到。","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":90,"line_end":92}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiao_ma","name":"小马","alias":["渔怒的小马"],"identity":"江湖侠客","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"脾气暴躁的年轻侠客，外号渔怒的小马","personality":{"traits":["倔强","骄傲","叛逆","痛苦","勇敢","直率"],"speech_style":"直来直去，不拐弯抹角，语气生硬","temperament":"暴躁易怒，内心脆弱"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ding_xi","type":"挚友","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"曾经形影不离，因丁喜成婚而疏远"},{"target":"char_lan_lan","type":"对手","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"从被迫护卫到暗昦纠缠"}],"known_skills":["skill_fen_nu_quan_fa"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[2],"source_refs":[{"chapter":2,"line_start":14,"line_end":14,"text":"小马故意露出牙齿猛笑，道：“还等什么？”"},{"chapter":2,"line_start":76,"line_end":76,"text":"你叫小马，别人都叫你渔怒的小马，因为你的脾气比谁都大。"}]},{"id":"char_lan_lan","name":"蓝兰","alias":[],"identity":"富家千金，客栈老板","faction":"无","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"美丽富有的年轻女子，父母双亡留下大笔遗产","personality":{"traits":["精明","大胆","婩媚","聪明","有心计","温柔"],"speech_style":"从容不迫，善于引导话题","temperament":"外柔内刚，善于掌控局面"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_ma","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"从互相试探到暗昦"},{"target":"char_lan_lan_de_di_di","type":"亲属","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"姐弟情深，为弟治病不惜冒险"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[2],"source_refs":[{"chapter":2,"line_start":100,"line_end":100,"text":"“我姓蓝。”她忽然说出了自己的名字：“我叫蓝兰。”"},{"chapter":2,"line_start":106,"line_end":106,"text":"蓝兰却不一点生气，又道：“我的父母都死了，却留给我很大一笔钱。”"}]},{"id":"char_lan_lan_de_di_di","name":"蓝兰的弟弟","alias":[],"identity":"病人","faction":"无","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"蓝兰的弟弟，身患重病需到西城就医","personality":{"traits":["体弱","需要照顾","姐姐的安全感","重病患者","被保护者"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lan_lan","type":"亲属","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"被姐姐保护，急需救治"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[2],"source_refs":[{"chapter":2,"line_start":224,"line_end":224,"text":"蓝兰道：“我弟弟有病，可能一辈子都医不好，如果不能在三天之内赶到西城，也许他就死定了。”"}]},{"id":"char_ding_xi","name":"丁喜","alias":["聪明的丁喜"],"identity":"小马的好友","faction":"无","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"小马的好友，聪明过人，已成婚","personality":{"traits":["聪明","稳重","重情重义","好友志气","智豫双全"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"未知"},"re